3071	  naturality of the sheafification unit \(\eta\) against the presheaf identification \(\mathtt{PrPbComp}\),
3072	  one tensor factor at a time; bifunctoriality of \(\otimes\) (the interchange law) recombines the two
3073	  single-factor squares into the asserted equality.
3074	\end{proof}
